h Ends</p>
				<p>This calculator is useful for fabrication Industry, Process Equipmen=
t Manufacturing Industry, Pressure Vessel Manufacturing Industry, Piping In=
dustry, Sheet Metal Industry, Heavy Equipment Fabrication Industry or any s=
imilar Industry where cone fabrication works involved.</p>
